Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Making chocolate from cocoa beans is just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make the best chocolate ever with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Fuku's still not happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clap him in irons and read him this book from cover to cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if even that's not enough, I'll hammer the chocolate into his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka, I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any way I can help, just let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know any candy stores or places where they sell the ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...{sou desu ne}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember there was an ingredient shop for professionals near the marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You would?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...a secret from Fukube?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll show you where it is on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{oreki}{\an8}Aren't you forgetting someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.{annai shite}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you tell him either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On pain of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really wish you wouldn't glare at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Satoshi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed up at just the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a battle for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I don't need to be home in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the Viper 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using Raiden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only one I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he'd keep running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this how he always fought?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's definitely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During junior high, he only focused on winning the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wasn't picky about the way he played as long as it meant he'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he lost, he didn't even try to hide his frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{satoshi}{\an8}That wasn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was a really sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{satoshi}{\an8}Switch sides and let's go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he gonna dash above me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good game, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how vigorously you pull on the joystick, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about that game...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you rush at me like that at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In a battle between giant robots, close combat's the really exciting part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{sou}This is how he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's changed a lot from junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so nervous already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be only too happy to accept it, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a guy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{kai}Itchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, a block of chocolate to remember me by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From Oreki Tomoe, with heartfelt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.32,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnHarlem Clown\blur1.5\c&H606264&\fs200\frz327\org(1022,469)\frx10\fry4\b1\pos(1028,364)}Condolences
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}condolences.{愛 / 哀 pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Ibara's chocolate turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to sample lots of other chocolate to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you sampled as much as you could, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, after all that we were able to complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it means to put your heart into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the plan, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka can't get out of going to the Manga Lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so she'll probably just leave it in the clubroom for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Satoshi will be happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Today is Valentine's Day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has this rule against giving presents to people close to us during the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even on Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um...{overlap with prev line}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,mean?{dou na no}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's gonna snow today.{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What, seriously?{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I forgot my umbrella, too...{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
