Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, are you going to the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll wait in the library and see if this sleet stops or turns to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The clubroom's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara can't go because she has to be at the Manga Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,News travels fast, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard from Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With what? Jeez.
