Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Fukube is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't turn up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. What if something happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him about half an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I'll wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukube... you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sleet finally stopped, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It can wait until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, at least hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for carelessly leaving the room unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to say to Mayaka?{inb4 satoshi's trollin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The chocolate that Mayaka made...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see what happens if Ibara finds out her chocolate was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a fan of horror stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.96,signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HD6C9C9&\blur0.6\fs35\pos(587,63)}History of the Hanya mask
