Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Oreki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.26,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnFranKleinBold\blur0.7\fs45\pos(582,464)\c&H322D42&}Freshly waxed.\N{\c&H0C0F0C&} No entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't use the west stairway to reach the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this look straight to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks trapezoidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowered it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in a transparent plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,About this big, shaped like a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was here when I went to look for Fukube.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you return to the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Past five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to lock the door for just fifteen minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't blame yourself, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for being so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Ibara know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not be the nicest thing, but I'd prefer to look for it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Fukube and I checked this room and looked around the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We met by the stairs, so we came to the clubroom together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How long was that Artisan guy there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Artisan guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Artisan Workshop member.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to look for Fukube,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was already working on that poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was there, he might remember who came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he was the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would just hang around putting up a poster after committing theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,True that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking if I saw anyone pass by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any character—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the culprit is still on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, what clubs meet on the fourth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Classics Club, the Light Music Club, the Astrology Club and the Philosophy Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think only we and the Astrology people are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm surprised to see
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're actually trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the sleet comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would anyone do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, let's consider the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.29,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnBPreplay\blur0.6\b1\fs40\pos(640,218)\c&H101A1A&}General Use Room #5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Classics Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back our chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we just wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A box of Valentine's Day chocolate was taken from our clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for anyone who might know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would we even...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone pass by here between a quarter to five and five?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the discussion was getting kinda lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember exactly when,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but only Nakayama and Yoshiwara left the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Oda too, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three out of five?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone gone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Oda that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Nakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme make this clear, detective boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,None of 'em brought any chocolate back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, any of you seen any chocolate around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you just gotta rub salt into the wound, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we again?{sawakiguchi's first bg line, you can ignore the rest}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawakiguchi got angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to get Mayaka's chocolate back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just return to the classroom for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I should put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to reach the fourth floor other than the east stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Realistically speaking, only the freshly waxed west stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no sign anyone had used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you checked the girls' restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it'd be in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It might as well be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pretty much figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's only one place it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Mayaka—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The chocolate I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the classroom unlocked, and the chocolate was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make that face. It's nothing you should apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find the chocolate, even if I have to use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, how could I face Mayaka tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka should've been happy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nowhere near as emotional as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But please leave this to me. I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it with you around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Nakayama from the Astrology Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara's chocolate was quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to hide it under a guy's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you did, you couldn't move naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But a girl's uniform is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tie it to your leg, the skirt will hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deliver Ibara's chocolate to Satoshi today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me. Calm down and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, give me your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you Ibara's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've fulfilled the promise I made to Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who stole Ibara's chocolate.{i knew it}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard the chocolate was stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were the only one who'd do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After I talked to the Artisan guy, that confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he'd lowered the poster too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have said that unless you'd told him to lower the right side of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably waited in the guys' restroom on the third floor until Chitanda passed,
