Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was too big,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so you couldn't put it in your bag, nor was there another bag big enough in the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't risk running into Chitanda while escaping with it in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hesitate for one moment before breaking it into pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Last April, you helped me escape Chitanda using that Golden Web story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one got hurt there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you at least explain yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it was just a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have no choice but to punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For Chitanda and Ibara as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not get punched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna say it, but I guess I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm the dedicated type?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more of a hobbyist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People like that immerse themselves in a particular field,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and in that field they don't want to lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you different, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. I can never be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I've already stopped trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt something was off at the arcade too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going on about losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to dedicate myself to a bunch of things for the sake of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a real bore, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to win so much, but even if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a boring, nasty way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fun unless you have fun winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One day I realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicated myself to not dedicating myself to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had lots of fun since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was one problem left:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really nice. In a class of her own.{hoka ni nai}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream that she wants to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{dakedo da yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I dedicate myself to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with her, that much is for sure.{isshou ni itai}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to dedicate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all just for my own convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even considered her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think I'm a bit too selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't want to neglect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I let go of my easy-going style and accepted Mayaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd end up turning back into my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, that's what I'm scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you won't accept her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, and this year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only way not to accept a chocolate I couldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you hurt Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These things don't go as well for me as they do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda was the mistake in this equation between Mayaka and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who stole the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Last Valentine's Day I told Fuku that I'd wait for his answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was the anniversary of that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably has it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I've deceived you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay... I'm the one who let things escalate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when Oreki said that he thought one of the Astrology Club members had stolen it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was covering for Fuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could Fukube just act as if it got stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It pisses me off so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that I still love him pisses me off even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, let's go and eat a cake somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the whole story, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell Chitanda this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'd rather get punched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how you're gonna answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty stupid for someone so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should tell him, "I'm sorry. I didn't know anything about you."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could.{maa ienai na}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I delivered the chocolate to Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for everything you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
