Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:23:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:23:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:18.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}The situation is unscientific
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:22.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}A montage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:25.39,ED,,0,0,0,,Who's calling who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:29.60,ED,,0,0,0,,You look away when our eyes are about to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.44,ED top,,0,0,0,,I can feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.44,0:24:33.69,ED,,0,0,0,,Am I just imagining things? It's so cold of you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:39.24,ED,,0,0,0,,It takes talent to read minds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:40.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.11,0:24:41.74,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.20,0:24:43.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.95,0:24:44.79,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:53.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}I'll fix the fire of youth in your heart while I can
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:55.76,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}If we can do it today why leave it for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:25:01.34,ED,,0,0,0,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.34,0:25:06.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Look for the back of the boy, burdened with secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.06,0:25:07.73,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even today
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.02,0:25:12.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}You are a fantasy and I'm drawn to you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:16.48,ED,,0,0,0,,This growing curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:19.28,ED,,0,0,0,,There's no twist in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.28,0:25:20.70,ED,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.70,0:25:23.70,ED,,0,0,0,,It's so interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.70,0:25:26.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}But why?
